<div class="container">

	
	<div class="one-col-text">
		<h2>Costs</h2><div class="the-content"><p>When deciding on a senior living option, there are many things that contribute to the value you receive for your monthly rent. While there are tangible benefits such as a private apartment, three chef-prepared meals per day, transportation, daily engagement activities, 24-hour staffing and security and more, there are many less tangible but highly valuable aspects as well.</p></div><div class="button-grid"><a href="https://info.lcbseniorliving.com/schedule-a-call-the-residence-pearl-street"  target="_blank" rel="noopener"  class="button" >Speak to an Advisor</a><a href="https://www.lcbseniorliving.com/living-options/costs/"  class="button" >Learn More</a></div>	</div>
</div>
</section>
