	</div>
	
	<div class="container text-box-container">
		
		<div class="text-box-wrap">
		<div class="text-box content-text">
		<div class="inner">
			
			<h2>Great Assisted Living Care is Our Hallmark!</h2><div class="line"><span class="line-sep"></span></div><div class="description-text the-content"><p style="text-align: center;">We specialize in providing expert Assisted Living services. From support with activities of daily living (ADL) such as walking escorts, bathing, dressing or toileting, to more extensive needs, we tailor care to each individual to make life easier and more fulfilling.</p>
<ul>
<li style="text-align: left;">Personalized care plans to meet daily needs</li>
<li style="text-align: left;">Medication management and administration</li>
<li style="text-align: left;">Crushed medications</li>
<li style="text-align: left;">Oxygen assistance</li>
<li style="text-align: left;">Support and coordination of advanced care needs (with third parties)</li>
<li style="text-align: left;">All associates certified by the National Institute for Dementia Education (NIDE)</li>
<li style="text-align: left;">A continuum of care to meet evolving needs</li>
<li style="text-align: left;">And more!</li>
</ul></div><div class="button-grid"><a href="https://www.lcbseniorliving.com/living-option/assisted-living/"  class="button">Learn More</a></div>			
			
		</div>	
		</div>
		</div>
		
	</div>
	
