	<div class="container background-carousel-text">
	<div class="container-inner">
		
		<div class="text-box-wrap">
		<div class="text-box">
			
			<h2>Everyday Gourmet</h2><div class="line"><span class="line-sep"></span></div><div class="description-text the-content"><blockquote><p><em>&#8220;One cannot think well,<br />
love well, sleep well, </em><br />
<em>if one has not dined well.&#8221;</em></p>
<h6>&#8211; Virginia Woolf</h6>
</blockquote>
<p>The famed author&#8217;s words capture our culinary philosophy perfectly. We combine gourmet dining principles with variety, wellness and a true restaurant experience to put meal time in its rightful place at the center of a perfect day!</p>
