			<h2>Community Engagement</h2><div class="line"><span class="line-sep"></span></div><div class="description-text the-content"><p>Our residents have enjoyed rich life experiences, and our community&#8217;s Engagement Program is as unique as the individuals who live here. Your days will be full of opportunities for continuing education, culture, physical wellness and fun.</p>
<p>You can view our Independent and Assisted Living newsletter and calendar<strong><a href="https://www.bell-litho.com/connectedliving/calendars/1000104IL.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">here</a></strong>.</p>
